fulltitle: Iran-Contra: Final Report of the Independent Counsel
title: Iran-Contra: Final Report of the Independent Counsel
_filename: _Iran-Contra - Final Report of the Independent Counsel.mp4
description:
An audiobook reading of the "Final Report of the Independent Counsel for the Iran/Contra Investigation", "Investigations and Prosecutions" section of Volume 1. Full report can be found here: https://fas.org/irp/offdocs/walsh/

Narrated by Chris Abernathy (https://www.fiverr.com/provoman) and produced by D. Giglio for  'Our Hidden History'.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
